---
title: Mediterranean Falafel & Roast Veggie Couscous Bowl with Dill-Parsley Yoghurt Dressing & Almonds
description: Have a ball with dinner – a ball of lightly spiced chickpeas blended with parsley and coriander, that is! Yep, we’re talking about falafels! With couscous, herby yoghurt dressing, roasted almonds and bright veggies, they make a dinner that's got the lot.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mediterranean-falafel-roast-veggie-couscous-bowl-db633167.jpg
